Each box of 100% Botanical hair colour contains 2 packets for one to two application, depending on your hair length . Boil 3 cups of pure water. Empty out the packet of 100% Botanical hair colour in a non-metallic (glass or plastic) mixing bowl. Pour one/cup of boiled water into the powder, stirring continuously with a non metallic spoon or spatula to break the lumps. Add enough of the boiled water to obtain a honey like consistency of the paste. After that keep the mixture for 1-2 minutes for thicken and stabilize. Apply mixture at the crown of the head, coating all strands with the help of supplied brush or Fingers. Leave mixture on your head for 30-45 minutes.
